original_title: California Democrats threaten redistricting plan to eliminate GOP seats | Fox News
article_summary: California Democrats, led by Gov. Gavin Newsom, propose a redistricting plan to gain five additional congressional seats, potentially eliminating more than half of the current GOP-held districts. The plan faces criticism, with Republicans and some Democrats questioning its fairness and potential impact on bipartisan support for the Independent Citizens Redistricting Commission.</s>
